00:00:11.790 --> 00:00:14.840
Agar, siz bu ilovani professional 
muhitda yaratayotgan bo‘lsangiz,

00:00:14.840 --> 00:00:17.920
arraylist yoki massivdan
 foydalanishning farqi yo‘q.

