ishlatishni afzal deb hisoblar edim.

00:00:32.645 --> 00:00:36.050
Chunki qo‘shimcha so‘zlarni qo‘shayotganda 
massivni hajmini o‘zgartirish haqida 

00:00:36.050 --> 00:00:38.040
o‘ylamaslik ancha qulay.

00:00:38.040 --> 00:00:41.940
Bu mashqning birinchi qismida, ilovani
 o‘zgartirishingizni, ya’ni words 

00:00:41.940 --> 00:00:45.810
massivida emas ArrayListda 
saqlashingizni xohlayman. 

00:00:45.810 --> 00:00:47.710
Hozir, so‘zlar bir xil turishlari kerak.

00:00:47.710 --> 00:00:51.370
Bular birdan o‘ngacha yozilgan sonlar
 bo‘lishi kerak, va aytgancha

00:00:51.370 --> 00:00:52.900
log xatlari yangilanishini
 ham nazoratga olishni unutmang. 

